author: dildick
body:
#### PR description:

With this PR we add histograms for CSC trigger primitives (ALCT, CLCT, LCT) data vs emulator comparisons. There are 1D histograms for each TP property and "data-emulator" plots - which ideally are empty. Backport needed for next MWGRs.

#### PR validation:

Code compiles.

#### if this PR is a backport please specify the original PR and why you need to backport that PR:

Backport of https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/33085
title: Data vs emulator plots in CSC DQM [11_2_X]
